11:44.304 --> 11:46.471
But look at the bright side,
you know,

11:46.473 --> 11:48.373
If you do sleep with gigi
and then the band breaks up

11:48.375 --> 11:50.141
And she leaves you behind,

11:50.143 --> 11:51.876
You got a great name
for a chain of hair salons.

11:53.980 --> 11:55.547
Mr. Gigi's.

12:05.492 --> 12:07.559
Hey.
What about that?

12:07.561 --> 12:08.893
No.

12:10.063 --> 12:12.731
Got nothin'.

12:12.733 --> 12:15.200
I can't tell
if you're joking or not.

12:15.202 --> 12:17.068
[inhales sharply]

12:17.070 --> 12:18.570
[blows raspberry]

12:18.572 --> 12:21.740
