[slurps]
[pen clicking]

12:37.257 --> 12:39.190
[piano note plays]

12:39.192 --> 12:40.525
[slurps]
[pen clicking]

12:40.527 --> 12:42.427
Can you stop doing
the pen thing?

12:42.429 --> 12:44.929
[slurping]

12:47.367 --> 12:48.399
[slurps]

12:48.401 --> 12:50.935
[sighs]

12:50.937 --> 12:52.203
How's it goin'?

12:52.205 --> 12:53.371
Do you want
some weed?

12:53.373 --> 12:54.906
Not funny.

12:54.908 --> 12:56.574
